text: Ani warra haqaan ala dachii keessatti boonan keeyyattoota kiyya irraa garan galchaYoo mallattoolee hunda arganis isatti hin amananuYoo karaa qajeelaa argan isa karaa hin godhatanuYoo karaa jallinaa argan isa karaa godhatuKun waan isaan keeyyattoota keenya kijibsiisaniifi ishee irraas dagatoo turaniifi
